籤詩版本二:
Huli nā manu ʻai i pengs i ka hāʻule, hauʻoli i ka huakaʻi a lele
E lele ana i mau tausani mile i ka lewa, ʻaʻole hiki i nā manu ʻē aʻe a pau
詩意:
ʻO kēia hexagram he hōʻailona o nā piʻi a me lalo o Kunpeng.
Hoʻololi nā mea a pau.
解曰: Ua lilo ʻo Kun i Peng. ʻAʻole hiki i nā tausani manu. He kinamona. E mahuahua ka waiwai a me ka waiwai.
籤詩故事一:
◇ ʻO Han Xin ke kuleana
ʻO Han Xin no Huaiyin.
I kela manawa, ua puhi ke Alii o Han i ke alanui papa, a ua hee ka nui o kona mau koa, a ua holo aku la o Han Xin, ka mea i puuhonua mua me ke Alii o Han.
Ua ʻike ʻo Xiao He a alualu iā Han Xin i ka pō.
I kekahi lā aʻe, i ka ʻike ʻana o ke aliʻi o Han no kēia mea, ʻōlelo ʻo ia me ka huhū: "Aneane ka hapalua o nā koa i holo.
Ua ʻōlelo ʻo Xiao He: "Inā ʻaʻohe manaʻo o kou mōʻī e lanakila iā Xiang Yu, e poina.
Ua kōkua ʻo Han Xin i ka Emepera Gao o Han e noho aliʻi i ka honua, hopu i ke aliʻi o Wei, lanakila iā Zhao, hāʻawi iā Yan, hopu iā Qi, a luku iā Chu. Ua hana ʻo ia i ʻumi mau hana nui a ua hāʻawi mua ʻia ka inoa ʻo King of Chu.
聖意: Pōmaikaʻi no ka home, laki maikaʻi iā ʻoe iho, laki maikaʻi no ka hāʻule, ʻoihana maikaʻi, male male hope, pōʻino ma Liujia, poʻe keʻakeʻa i ka mahina ʻai, ʻano kilika, palahalaha, laki maikaʻi no nā holoholona ʻeono, laki maikaʻi i ka punawai, nalowale. kanaka, hoʻopiʻi, kūleʻa, neʻe, conservativeness, nalowale waiwai, maʻi, pule no ka maluhia ma nā mauna a me nā lua kupapaʻu.
古人: Hana ʻo Han Xin i ke kuleana
